<body>
  <h2>What is the CSC code?</h2>
  <p>For your safety and security, we require that you enter your Card Security Code (CSC).</p>
  <div>
    <div class="card">
      <p>For <strong>MasterCard, Visa,</strong> and <strong>Discover,</strong> the CSC is the last three digits in the signature area on the back of your card.</p>
      <p><img src="/sitepics/cv_card.gif" border="0" alt=""></p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <p>For <strong>American Express,</strong> the CSC is a group of four digits on front of the card.</p>
      <p><img src="/sitepics/cv_amex_card.gif" border="0" alt=""></p>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div>
  </div>
  <p class="close"><a href="#" onClick="window.close();return false;">Close Window</a></p>
</body>
